{"type": "article", "id": 22880, "title": "小池和也的酒器设计", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-26T07:30:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 75, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016070213545895kzvUnobEhwOTYI.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是日本设计师小池和也的一组酒器设计，杯体有陶瓷和玻璃杯两种，搭配 Yoshino 雪松木的盖子，有一种日式的温润触感。陶瓷制的杯子有白色和黑色，都没有任何花纹，简洁干净。对比之下，盖子上的木纹则更加自然了。松木盖子也可以当做酒杯，喝的时候能感受到松木的清香。<a href=\"http://en.doogdesign.jp/project/yoshino/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021354562vBRtHu7OXQp0wTV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135457o4biItY1fy7HZmhs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135457xvz2TeEy83gLVSR4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135457kKSiAfrtFgyx7c9D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135458Q9yZhloneVjaqB0M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}